{
  "texts": [
    "Second, there are technical risks.",
    "Artificial intelligence technology itself may also have some technical risks, such as the accuracy and stability of algorithms, network and data security issues, especially the application of generative AI technology, the content generated may appear \"fabricated\" content, thus misleading users.",
    "[20]It is necessary for financial institutions to establish a sound technical risk management system and technical safeguard measures for prevention and management to ensure the stability and security in the application of artificial intelligence technology.",
    "Third, there are legal risks.",
    "The application of artificial intelligence in the financial industry may involve some legal issues, such as the identification of responsibility for market risks caused by wrong decisions caused by artificial intelligence technology, and corresponding management systems and processes need to be established."
  ]
}